  "texts": [
    "The data results confirm that the model can effectively learn features for the classification of breaking news authenticity, and each module plays a positive role.",
    "Threshold studyIn this section of the experiment, we conducted a study on parameters influencing the model's performance.",
    "Among the three modules of the model, variations in the semantic feature space size of the cross-modal feature extraction module and the feature space size of the domain discriminator in the domain detection module have minimal impact on the model's detection performance, and we won't delve into detailed discussions here.",
